VALUES (N'TEC-APL-IP16PM-256GB-DES-220', N'Apple iPhone 16 Pro Max (256GB, Desert Titanium, Unlocked)', 1199, 33, N'Apple iPhone 16 Pro Max (256GB, Desert Titanium, Unlocked). The ultimate flagship device with a glorious 6.9-inch screen and A18 Pro chip. Retail grade stock curated for USA shoppers.', N'The pinnacle of mobile hardware engineering. Wrapped inside an aerospace-grade Grade 5 titanium chassis, this device features a stunning 6.9-inch Super Retina XDR screen with ultra-thin bezels. Powered by the A18 Pro chip with custom Neural Engine for seamless AI tasks, combined with an advanced telephoto camera, and tactile physical camera slider control. This premium bundle features an optimized setup with hand-selected Desert Titanium aesthetics and configured 256GB physical specifications. Packaged inside impact-cushioned freight storage containers with certificates of authenticity and fully guaranteed consumer services.', N'Tech & Electronics', N'{"Brand":"Apple","Model":"iPhone 16 Pro Max","Display":"6.9\" Super Retina XDR OLED","Processor":"A18 Pro","Chassis":"Grade 5 Titanium","Storage/Config":"256GB","Color Finish":"Desert Titanium","Standard Inventory Group":"USA Retail Center"}');
INSERT INTO dbo.Products (SKU, Name, Price, Stock, ShortDescription, LongDescription, Category, Specifications)
VALUES (N'TEC-SAM-S25U-256GB-TIT-221', N'Samsung Galaxy S25 Ultra 5G (256GB, Titanium Gray, Unlocked)', 1311.5, 37, N'Samsung Galaxy S25 Ultra 5G (256GB, Titanium Gray, Unlocked). The absolute zenith of Android mobile systems, built with Grade 5 titanium. Retail grade stock curated for USA shoppers.', N'Uncompromising Android performance. Powered by the hyper-efficient Snapdragon 8 Gen 4 AI-optimized processor. Showcases an incredibly bright 6.8-inch Dynamic AMOLED 2X flat display. Complete with integrated high-fidelity S-Pen, a 200MP detail crop main lens, and advanced real-time language translations. This premium bundle features an optimized setup with hand-selected Titanium Gray aesthetics and configured 256GB physical specifications. Packaged inside impact-cushioned freight storage containers with certificates of authenticity and fully guaranteed consumer services.', N'Tech & Electronics', N'{"Brand":"Samsung","Model":"Galaxy S25 Ultra","Display":"6.8\" Dynamic AMOLED 2X","Processor":"Snapdragon 8 Gen 4","Stylus":"S-Pen Included","Storage/Config":"256GB","Color Finish":"Titanium Gray","Standard Inventory Group":"USA Retail Center"}');
INSERT INTO dbo.Products (SKU, Name, Price, Stock, ShortDescription, LongDescription, Category, Specifications)
VALUES (N'TEC-APL-MBP14-512GB-SPA-222', N'Apple MacBook Pro 14-inch M4 Pro (512GB SSD, Space Black, Unlocked)', 2024, 41, N'Apple MacBook Pro 14-inch M4 Pro (512GB SSD, Space Black, Unlocked). Hyper-efficient professional power in a portable 14-inch form factor. Retail grade stock curated for USA shoppers.', N'Engineered for designers, developers, and creators. The Apple MacBook Pro runs on the custom-silicon M4 Pro chip with a 14-core CPU and 20-core GPU. Outfitted with Liquid Retina XDR display yielding up to 1600 nits peak luminance and high-speed Thunderbolt 4 physical interfaces. This premium bundle features an optimized setup with hand-selected Space Black aesthetics and configured 512GB SSD physical specifications. Packaged inside impact-cushioned freight storage containers with certificates of authenticity and fully guaranteed consumer services.', N'Tech & Electronics', N'{"Brand":"Apple","Model":"MacBook Pro 14\"","Display":"14.2\" Liquid Retina XDR","Processor":"Apple M4 Pro","Battery":"Up to 22 Hours","Storage/Config":"512GB SSD","Color Finish":"Space Black","Standard Inventory Group":"USA Retail Center"}');
